author: @shanghainewbison7687
text: Another way to change the dtype of df["YearsCode"].  def change_to_float(string):     try:         result = float(string)     except:         result = np.nan     finally:         return result   df['YearsCode'] = df['YearsCode'].apply(change_to_float) df['YearsCode'].mean()
